trans-unit.source: Represents a <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority" /> property (and its value) of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: Rappresenta una proprietà <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority" /> (e il relativo valore) di un componente hardware o software del sistema di stampa.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inizializza una nuova istanza della classe <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty" />.

trans-unit.source: The name of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority" /> property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty" /> represents.
trans-unit.target: Nome della proprietà <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority" /> rappresentata dall'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty" /> class for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: Inizializza una nuova istanza della classe <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty" /> per la proprietà specificata.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: Il `attributeName` devono essere digitati esattamente come il nome di determinate <xref:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority> proprietà di un oggetto di sistema di stampa, comprese le maiuscole e minuscole.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Priority%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object must be spelled "Priority", not "JobPriority".
trans-unit.target: Ad esempio, il <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Priority%2A> proprietà di un <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> oggetto deve essere digitato "Priority", anziché "JobPriority".

trans-unit.source: The name of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority" /> property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty" /> represents.
trans-unit.target: Nome della proprietà <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority" /> rappresentata dall'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty" />.

trans-unit.source: The value of the property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty" /> represents.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty" /> class that has the specified value for the specified attribute.
trans-unit.target: Inizializza una nuova istanza della classe <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty" /> con il valore specificato per l'attributo specificato.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: Il `attributeName` devono essere digitati esattamente come il nome di determinate <xref:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority> proprietà di un oggetto di sistema di stampa, comprese le maiuscole e minuscole.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Priority%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object must be spelled "Priority", not "JobPriority".
trans-unit.target: Ad esempio, il <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Priority%2A> proprietà di un <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> oggetto deve essere digitato "Priority", anziché "JobPriority".

trans-unit.source: Provides implicit conversion from a <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty" /> (or from a pointer to such a property) to a <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority" />.
trans-unit.target: Fornisce la conversione implicita da un oggetto <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty" /> (o da un puntatore a tale proprietà) a un oggetto <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority" />.

trans-unit.source: A pointer to the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintBooleanProperty" /> that is converted.
Provides implicit conversion to a <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority" /> from a pointer to a <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty" />.
trans-unit.target: Fornisce la conversione implicita a un oggetto <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority" /> da un puntatore a un oggetto <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the value of the property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty" /> represents.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene o imposta il valore della proprietà rappresentata dall'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty" />.
